headline: Triumph Financial (TFIN) Lags Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Triumph Financial (TFIN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -50% and 6.04%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
